data.name: label7.Text
data.value: 1 .After logging in, click the "Compose" button on the top left. 2 .Enter the recipient’s email address in the "To" field. 3 .Type a subject for the email in the "Subject" field. 4 .Write your message in the large text box below. 5 .Click "Send".

data.name: label3.Text
data.value: 1 .Go to Gmail: Visit www.gmail.com. 2 .Sign Up: Click on "Create account" and choose "For myself" or "For business" depending on your need. 3 .Fill in Information: Enter your First and Last Name. Choose a Username (your email address will be [username]@gmail.com). Create a Password and confirm it. 4 .Verify Your Phone Number: Google will send a code via SMS to verify your identity. 5 .Fill in Personal Info: Provide a recovery email if you forget your email, your birth date, and gender. 6 .Agree to Terms: Read and accept Google's terms and privacy policy.
